#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "AqBanking backend"
#~ msgstr "Zaledje AqBanking"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An import backend for Skrooge using AqBanking.\\n You must install "
#~ "AqBanking (aqbanking-cli) and setup all accounts manually before using "
#~ "this backend.\\n\\nAt least AqBanking version 5.6.10 or later is required."
#~ "\\n\\nThis backend starts an AqBanking user-interactive session in the "
#~ "default terminal emulator.\\nIf you experience issues please switch to "
#~ "the \"xterm\" terminal emulator by setting the parameters to:"
#~ "\\naqbanking(--terminal-emulator '\"xterm -e\"') [Note: The single and "
#~ "double quotes are important!]\\n\\nFor a list of all parameters please "
#~ "run \"skrooge-sabb.py bulkdownload --help\"."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Uvozno zaledje za Skrooge z uporabo AqBanking.\\n Pred uporabo tega "
#~ "zaledja morate namestiti AqBanking (aqbanking-cli) in nastaviti vse "
#~ "račune ročno.\\n\\nPotrebna je najmanj različica AqBanking 5.6.10 ali "
#~ "novejša.\\n\\nTo zaledje zažene uporabniško interaktivno sejo aqBanking v "
#~ "privzetem emulatorju terminala.\\nČe imate težave, prenesite na emulator "
#~ "terminala »xterm«, tako da parametre nastavite na:\\naqbanking(--terminal-"
#~ "emulator '\"xterm -e\") [Opomba:  Pomembni so enojni in dvojni "
#~ "narekovaji!] \\n\\nZa seznam vseh parametrov zaženite »skrooge-sabb.py "
#~ "bulkdownload —help«."

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "Weboob coming backend"
#~ msgstr "Zaledje weboob za »coming«"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An import backend for Skrooge using weboob for coming operation. This "
#~ "plugin can be used for card with deferred debit.\\n You must install "
#~ "weboob and configure correctly the boobank module before using this "
#~ "backend.\\n\\n Parameter:\\n The list of accounts to import separated by "
#~ "'|'. If you don't pass parameter then all accounts will be imported.\\n "
#~ "Example: 123@ca|456@bp"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Uvozno zaledje za Skrooge, ki uporablja weboob za operacije »coming«. Ta "
#~ "vtičnik lahko uporabite za kartico z odloženo bremenitvijo.\\n Pred "
#~ "uporabo te kartice morate namestiti weboob in pravilno prilagoditi modul "
#~ "boobank.\\n\\n Parameter:\\n Seznam računov za uvoz, ločen z »|«. Če "
#~ "parametra ne prenesete, bodo uvoženi vsi računi.\\n Primer: 123@ca|456@bp"

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "Weboob backend"
#~ msgstr "Zaledje weboob"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An import backend for Skrooge using weboob.\\n You must install weboob "
#~ "and configure correctly the boobank module before using this backend.\\n"
#~ "\\n Parameters:\\n 1-The list of accounts to import separated by '|'. If "
#~ "you don't pass parameter then all accounts will be imported.\\n Example: "
#~ "123@ca|456@bp\\n 2-The first date of imported transactions in format YYYY-"
#~ "MM-DD.\\n Example: 2017-09-25\\nWarning:If you want to specify this "
#~ "parameter, you have to specify the first one too but it could be blank."
#~ "\\n Example: ,2017-09-25"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Uvozno zaledje za Skrooge z uporabo weboob.\\n Pred uporabo tega zaledja "
#~ "morate namestiti weboob in pravilno prilagoditi modul boobank.\\n\\n "
#~ "Parametri:\\n 1-Seznam računov za uvoz, ločen z '|'. Če ne prenesete "
#~ "parametra, bodo vsi računi uvoženi.\\n Primer: 123@ca|456@bp\\n 2-Prvi "
#~ "datum uvoženih operacij v obliki LLLL-MM-DD.\\n Primer: "
#~ "2017-09-25\\nPozor: Če želite določiti ta parameter, morate navesti tudi "
#~ "prvi parameter, ki pa je lahko prazen.\\n Primer: ,2017-09-25"

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "Woob coming backend"
#~ msgstr "Zaledje woob za »coming«"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An import backend for Skrooge using woob for coming operation. This "
#~ "plugin can be used for card with deferred debit.\\n You must install woob "
#~ "and configure correctly the bank module before using this backend.\\n\\n "
#~ "Parameter:\\n The list of accounts to import separated by '|'. If you "
#~ "don't pass parameter then all accounts will be imported.\\n Example: "
#~ "123@ca|456@bp"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Uvozno zaledje za Skrooge z uporabo woob za operacijo »coming«. Ta "
#~ "vtičnik lahko uporabite za kartice z odloženim plačilom.\\n Morate "
#~ "namestiti woob in pravilno prilagoditi bančni modul, preden uporabite to "
#~ "zaledje.\\n\\n Parameter:\\n Seznam računov za uvoz, ločen z »|«. Če "
#~ "parametra ne podate, bodo uvoženi vsi računi.\\n Primer: 123@ca|456@bp"

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "Woob backend"
#~ msgstr "Zaledje woob"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An import backend for Skrooge using woob.\\n You must install woob and "
#~ "configure correctly the bank module before using this backend.\\n\\n "
#~ "Parameters:\\n 1-The list of accounts to import separated by '|'. If you "
#~ "don't pass parameter then all accounts will be imported.\\n Example: "
#~ "123@ca|456@bp\\n 2-The first date of imported transactions in format YYYY-"
#~ "MM-DD.\\n Example: 2017-09-25\\nWarning:If you want to specify this "
#~ "parameter, you have to specify the first one too but it could be blank."
#~ "\\n Example: ,2017-09-25\\n 3-The woob additional options (example: --nss)"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Uvozno zaledje za Skrooge z uporabo woob.\\n Namestiti morate woob in "
#~ "pravilno prilagoditi bančni modul, preden uporabite to zaledje.\\n\\n "
#~ "Parametri:\\n 1-Seznam računov za uvoz, ločen z '|'. Če ne prenesete "
#~ "parametra, bodo uvoženi vsi računi.\\n Primer: 123@ca|456@bp\\n 2-Prvi "
#~ "datum uvoženih operacij v obliki LLLL-MM-DD.\\n Primer: "
#~ "2017-09-25\\nPozor: Če želite določiti ta parameter, morate navesti tudi "
#~ "prvega, ali pa ga navesti kot praznega.\\n Primer: ,2017-09-25\\n 3-"
#~ "Dodatne možnosti za woob (primer: --nss)"

